  <entry>
    <title>Ignore diacritical marks in search</title>
    <link href="https://blog.yskz.dev/2023/02/17/ignore-diacritical-marks-in-search/"/>
    <id>https://blog.yskz.dev/2023/02/17/ignore-diacritical-marks-in-search/</id>
    <published>2023-02-17T07:43:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-02-17T19:36:32.300Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Search ignores marks like tilde(like letter ‘n’ with upper wave in <em>España</em>).</p><span id="more"></span><p>Japanese dakuten(だくてん) and handakuten(はんだくてん) are kind of diacritical mark.</p><p>Search also ignores cases aka small or capital letters.</p><ol><li>This Hexo plugin code is:</li></ol><pre class="language-nunjuks" data-language="nunjuks"><code class="language-nunjuks">&#123;% asset_img search-box.svg Search box %&#125;</code></pre><p>To show below image:</p><img src="/2023/02/17/ignore-diacritical-marks-in-search/search-box.svg" class="" title="Search box"><ol start="2"><li>(1.) is an image short code of:</li></ol><pre class="language-markup" data-language="markup"><code class="language-markup"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>&#123;% asset_path search-box.svg %&#125;<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">alt</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>Search box<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><img src="/2023/02/17/ignore-diacritical-marks-in-search/search-box.svg" alt="Search box"><ol start="3"><li>Marked _config.html</li></ol><pre class="language-yaml" data-language="yaml"><code class="language-yaml"><span class="token key atrule">post_asset_folder</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true</span><span class="token key atrule">marked</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>  <span class="token key atrule">prependRoot</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true</span>  <span class="token key atrule">postAsset</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true</span></code></pre><p>Enables markdown:</p><pre class="language-markdown" data-language="markdown"><code class="language-markdown">![](search-box.svg)</code></pre><p><img src="search-box.svg" alt=""></p><ol start="4"><li>Embed an image in the document</li></ol><svg viewBox="0 0 500 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">  <rect x="65.496" y="67.168" width="185.619" height="255.853" style="fill: rgb(216, 216, 216); stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);"/>  <rect x="74.972" y="118.45" width="98.105" height="25.084" style="fill: rgb(216, 216, 216); stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);"/>  <ellipse style="fill: rgb(216, 216, 216); stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);" cx="220.178" cy="130.156" rx="18.116" ry="10.033"/>  <rect x="93.924" y="170.847" width="124.303" height="57.971" style="fill: rgb(216, 216, 216); stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);"/>  <rect x="93.367" y="237.18" width="124.303" height="57.971" style="fill: rgb(216, 216, 216); stroke: rgb(0, 0, 0);"/>  <text style="white-space: pre; fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19.5px;" x="96.154" y="135.73">Input</text>  <text style="white-space: pre; fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19.5px;" x="182.553" y="111.204">Submit</text>  <text style="white-space: pre; fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19.5px;" x="119.565" y="194.816">Reslut 1</text>  <text style="white-space: pre; fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19.5px;" x="119.008" y="259.476">Result 2</text>  <text style="white-space: pre; fill: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19.5px;" x="69.955" y="40.412">Search box</text></svg>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Search ignores marks like tilde(like letter ‘n’ with upper wave in &lt;em&gt;España&lt;/em&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
